Biology: Grows on a variety of substrates like other hydroids (especially
Tubularia indivisa
), tubes of polychaetes, and ascidians. Depth range of reliablyidentified material 6-750 m , usually below 80 m in boreal regions.

The identities of records from deep waters of the Gulf of Gascogne and the Azores (
Leloup, 1940
; 
Vervoort, 1985
) are uncertain.
